{"about_the_game":"Juicy army is the sweetest action roguelike set in a dream universe where you'll have to fight an army of juicy creatures!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Prologue Features:</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/extras/Scenery.png?t=1621299922\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Discover a world full of delicious treats! This fantasy kingdom is made of sweet and delightful objects! There are 5 biomes - Strawberry, Cheese, Candy,  Donut, and Chocolate.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/extras/Enemies.png?t=1621299922\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Exotic fruity enemies! There are flying grapes, bouncing orange, sniper apple, pineapple bandit, and a lot of other juicy creatures. But don't let their cute appearance fool you! They may look cute, but they can get vicious quickly!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/extras/Weapons.png?t=1621299922\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> As you progress, you'll find loads of interesting weapons. <br></li><li> Throughout your journey, you'll unlock new items, each with different strengths. Harness the power of these new abilities and smash through all obstacles!<br></li><li> Responsive, fluid, and fun to play combat system!<br></li><li> Procedurally generated worlds blended with handcrafted design elements to keep each run fresh and unique.<br></li><li> Beautiful and adorable art style!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1621299922","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1621299922","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1621299922","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1621299922","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>FULL GAME</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Juicy army is the sweetest action roguelike set in a dream universe where you'll have to fight an army of juicy creatures!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Prologue Features:</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/extras/Scenery.png?t=1621299922\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Discover a world full of delicious treats! This fantasy kingdom is made of sweet and delightful objects! There are 5 biomes - Strawberry, Cheese, Candy,  Donut, and Chocolate.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/extras/Enemies.png?t=1621299922\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Exotic fruity enemies! There are flying grapes, bouncing orange, sniper apple, pineapple bandit, and a lot of other juicy creatures. But don't let their cute appearance fool you! They may look cute, but they can get vicious quickly!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1153060/extras/Weapons.png?t=1621299922\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> As you progress, you'll find loads of interesting weapons. <br></li><li> Throughout your journey, you'll unlock new items, each with different strengths. Harness the power of these new abilities and smash through all obstacles!<br></li><li> Responsive, fluid, and fun to play combat system!<br></li><li> Procedurally generated worlds blended with handcrafted design elements to keep each run fresh and unique.<br></li><li> Beautiful and adorable art style!</li></ul>","developers":["Taptroise"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":